    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A glassy blue mineral, named for its copper content and its similarity to rivaite, that is a component of the artificial inorganic pigment, Egyptian blue.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
